          - paragraph [ref=e340]: We are all the guardians of our amazing planet, and we believe travel should be considered, mindful, responsible. A force for good. Every trip you book with us supports the initiatives of A&K Philanthropy, positively impacting communities and conservation efforts in the places where we travel.
          - paragraph [ref=e341]: A&K founder Geoffrey Kent pioneered the community-first approach to conservation more than 60 years ago. Today, A&K Philanthropy is a global nonprofit organization spanning all seven continents, committed to improving lives and helping preserve some of the world’s most precious ecosystems, through impact projects aligned with UN Sustainable Development Goals.
